Package: fldgen
Type: Package
Title: Generate Temperature Fields with Spatial and Temporal Correlation
Version: 2.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Robert", "Link", email = "robert.link@pnnl.gov", role = c("aut", "cre", "ard")),
	     person("Abigail", "Snyder", email = "abigail.snyder@pnnl.gov", role = c("aut", "lyr")),
	     person("Kalyn", "Dorheim", email = "kalyn.dorheim@pnnl.gov", role = c("ctg")))
Description: Provides functions to learn the spatial and temporal correlation of the
    variability in an ESM and generate random temperature fields or random joint temperature
	and precipitation fields with equivalent properties.
